Bring water to a boil in a small saucepan. Stir in oats and salt. Cook, stirring occasionally, over medium heat 5 minutes. Serve with toppings, if desired. Sprinkle 2 teaspoons SPLENDA Brown Sugar Blend and 2 tablespoons fresh or frozen blueberries over hot cooked oatmeal. Drizzle with 1 tablespoon fat-free half-and-half.